title: Inside The Parker - Nats Steal Game 1; Rob's World Series Prediction; A.J. Pierzynski Breaks Down Nationals/Astros
itunes:title: Inside The Parker - Nats Steal Game 1; Rob's World Series Prediction; A.J. Pierzynski Breaks Down Nationals/Astros
description:
This week on Inside the (Rob) Parker, Rob reacts to the Nationals taking Game 1 of the World Series against Houston and gets a World Series breakdown with Fox MLB Analyst, and former longtime MLB catcher A.J. Pierzynski. He also gives the Analytic of The Week, and debates a hot MLB topic in Foul or Fair. Follow Rob on Twitter and subscribe, rate and listen to get the latest!
